<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.3.3">
<l>ūrnta cakaṭa mutaitta pātattaṉ pēymulai</l>
<l>cārntu cuvaitta cevvāya ṉeṉṉai niṟaikoṇṭāṉ</l>
<l>pērntum peyarntu mavaṉō ṭaṉṟiyōr collilēṉ</l>
<l>ṟīrntaveṉ ṟōḻī yeṉceyyu mūravar kavvaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I don’t have one word except for him, although he separates over and again,</l>
<l>he who took me to the full, the one with red mouth who closely tasted</l>
<l>the breast of the demoness, he whose foot kicked the cart that moved,</l>
<l>o friend of me who is at an end. What will the gossip of the villagers do?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
